Because I love you

14:40.839 --> 14:42.882
and I love your little feet.

14:42.923 --> 14:44.300
What's going on?

14:44.342 --> 14:48.095
Daddy loves me and he

14:44.342 --> 14:48.095
loves my little feet.

14:48.137 --> 14:50.931
I want to preserve

14:48.137 --> 14:50.931
every minute of your lives.

14:50.973 --> 14:52.559
I'm gonna go brush my teeth.

14:52.600 --> 14:53.810
Do you want to reload?

14:54.853 --> 14:56.145
Wait a minute, D.J.

14:56.187 --> 14:58.981
Girls, I have

14:56.187 --> 14:58.981
a surprise for you.

14:59.023 --> 15:01.025
I am not going to work today.

15:01.067 --> 15:03.862
Today is father-daughter

15:01.067 --> 15:03.862
day, part two.

15:03.903 --> 15:06.698
- Yay!

15:03.903 --> 15:06.698
- 'Yay!'

