I worked it out.

15:12.203 --> 15:13.830
I'm working New Year's Eve

15:13.872 --> 15:15.540
but I worked it out.

15:15.582 --> 15:16.833
This is your day.

15:16.875 --> 15:18.084
We can do whatever

15:16.875 --> 15:18.084
you want to do.

