Then can we go horseback riding?

15:26.426 --> 15:27.635
It's your day.

15:27.677 --> 15:29.053
Then can we buy a big-screen TV

15:29.095 --> 15:31.222
a CD player,

15:29.095 --> 15:31.222
and a couple of mopeds?

15:34.141 --> 15:37.771
Why don't I just get

15:34.141 --> 15:37.771
you your own MasterCard?

15:37.812 --> 15:39.480
Ooh, it is my day.

