Hello. Joey!

15:44.110 --> 15:45.403
You've been gone

15:44.110 --> 15:45.403
since yesterday.

15:45.445 --> 15:47.739
You get your butt

15:45.445 --> 15:47.739
back here right now..

15:47.781 --> 15:50.157
..."Chill out, babe"?

15:50.199 --> 15:51.910
Listen, you little

15:50.199 --> 15:51.910
